  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/609e51641181cffaa32ec43a32e42a33.poster.avif?t=1773139663\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/609e51641181cffaa32ec43a32e42a33.webm?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/609e51641181cffaa32ec43a32e42a33.mp4?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Everdine - A Lost Girl’s Tale</strong> is a short, atmospheric, fairy tale vibes RPG Maker horror adventure game. <br><br>Everdine finds herself lost in a forest of eternal twilight. Soon to be hunted by a mysterious beast, she will stumble across the remnants of others that came before her, and learn of a magical ritual that may be her only way out. <br><br>Gather the needed ingredients to complete the spell, and bring her home before the dangers of these woods devour poor Everdine. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/db23d23b7cad794ed951952003f71082.poster.avif?t=1773139663\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/db23d23b7cad794ed951952003f71082.webm?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short, atmospheric game.  <br></li><li>Collect the needed items to escape an environment that tries to kill you.  <br></li><li>Progression through exploration, solving puzzles and overcoming other obstacles. <br></li><li>Uncover the mysteries of the forest. <br></li><li>A female protagonist.  <br></li><li>Inspired by folklore and fairy tales. <br></li><li>Neither much gore, nor an overuse of jump scares.<br></li><li>Multiple endings and death scenes. <br></li><li>It's been called wholesome horror and eerie but cute before.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/b78ed116fd7f136d562c364514ea9e41.poster.avif?t=1773139663\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/b78ed116fd7f136d562c364514ea9e41.webm?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/b78ed116fd7f136d562c364514ea9e41.mp4?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Warnings: <br>Flashing lights and images. <br>Play with sound on (some scenes depend on sound).",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/609e51641181cffaa32ec43a32e42a33.poster.avif?t=1773139663\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/609e51641181cffaa32ec43a32e42a33.webm?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/609e51641181cffaa32ec43a32e42a33.mp4?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Everdine - A Lost Girl’s Tale</strong> is a short, atmospheric, fairy tale vibes RPG Maker horror adventure game. <br><br>Everdine finds herself lost in a forest of eternal twilight. Soon to be hunted by a mysterious beast, she will stumble across the remnants of others that came before her, and learn of a magical ritual that may be her only way out. <br><br>Gather the needed ingredients to complete the spell, and bring her home before the dangers of these woods devour poor Everdine. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/db23d23b7cad794ed951952003f71082.poster.avif?t=1773139663\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/db23d23b7cad794ed951952003f71082.webm?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A short, atmospheric game.  <br></li><li>Collect the needed items to escape an environment that tries to kill you.  <br></li><li>Progression through exploration, solving puzzles and overcoming other obstacles. <br></li><li>Uncover the mysteries of the forest. <br></li><li>A female protagonist.  <br></li><li>Inspired by folklore and fairy tales. <br></li><li>Neither much gore, nor an overuse of jump scares.<br></li><li>Multiple endings and death scenes. <br></li><li>It's been called wholesome horror and eerie but cute before.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/b78ed116fd7f136d562c364514ea9e41.poster.avif?t=1773139663\" width=320 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/b78ed116fd7f136d562c364514ea9e41.webm?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1687710/extras/b78ed116fd7f136d562c364514ea9e41.mp4?t=1773139663\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br>Warnings: <br>Flashing lights and images. <br>Play with sound on (some scenes depend on sound).",
